4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals with no prior knowledge, aiming to develop skills needed to protect digital environments. The program spans 16 weeks with three live online classes each week, accommodating up to 16 students. Key topics include Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, as well as cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence. Participants will learn to manage risks and navigate compliance with international standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. Upon completion, students receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate. The curriculum is available in both English and Spanish. For more information, visit https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity. stop